<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Monarch Design — Where Brands Become Royalty</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Unbounded:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --black: #0A0A0A;
  --gold: #C9A84C;
  --gold-light: #E8C96A;
  --red: #B22222;
  --cream: #F5F0E8;
  --white: #FFFFFF;
  --gray: #888;
  --border: rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}

*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  cursor: none;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* CUSTOM CURSOR */
.cursor {
  position: fixed;
  width: 10px; height: 10px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9999;
  transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.2s;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}
.cursor-ring {
  position: fixed;
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.5);
  border-radius: 50%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9998;
  transition: transform 0.35s ease, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, opacity 0.2s;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}
body:has(a:hover) .cursor-ring,
body:has(button:hover) .cursor-ring { width: 56px; height: 56px; }

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  padding: 28px 60px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: border-color 0.4s, background 0.4s, padding 0.4s;
}
nav.scrolled {
  border-color: var(--border);
  background: rgba(10,10,10,0.95);
  padding: 18px 60px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}
.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--white);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 44px;
  list-style: none;
}
.nav-links a {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}
.nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.nav-cta {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--black);
  background: var(--gold);
  padding: 12px 24px;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }

/* HERO */
#hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 0 60px;
}
.hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: var(--black);
}
.hero-grid {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 80px 80px;
}
.hero-stripes {
  position: absolute;
  right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 42%;
  display: flex;
}
.hs-panel { flex: 1; }
.hs1 { background: #0e0e0e; }
.hs2 { background: #111; }
.hs-accent {
  position: absolute;
  right: 42%;
  top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 3px;
  background: var(--red);
}
.hs-accent2 {
  position: absolute;
  right: calc(42% + 6px);
  top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 1.5px;
  background: var(--gold);
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 700px;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s forwards;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 0.92;
  letter-spacing: -4px;
  color: var(--white);
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s forwards;
}
.hero-title .gold { color: var(--gold); }
.hero-title .red { color: var(--red); }
.hero-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 24px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
  margin-top: 28px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 480px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s forwards;
}
.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 48px;
  align-items: center;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s forwards;
}
.btn-primary {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--black);
  background: var(--gold);
  padding: 18px 36px;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
  display: inline-block;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.btn-secondary {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
}
.btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); }
.hero-stats {
  position: absolute;
  right: 60px;
  bottom: 80px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 32px;
  z-index: 2;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1s forwards;
}
.stat-item { text-align: right; }
.stat-num {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
}
.stat-num span { color: var(--gold); }
.stat-label {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.scroll-hint {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 40px;
  left: 60px;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1.2s forwards;
}
.scroll-line {
  width: 60px;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.scroll-line::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: -100%;
  top: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--gold);
  animation: scanLine 2s 1.5s infinite;
}
.scroll-text {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* MARQUEE */
.marquee-section {
  padding: 24px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--black);
}
.marquee-track {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.marquee-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 32px;
  padding: 0 40px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.marquee-text {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.marquee-dot {
  width: 5px; height: 5px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ABOUT */
#about {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
}
.about-label {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.about-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -2px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.about-body {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 19px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.about-body strong {
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 400;
}
.about-visual {
  position: relative;
  height: 500px;
}
.av-frame {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.av-inner {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 20px;
  background: #111;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.av-m {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 220px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(201,168,76,0.07);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -10px;
  user-select: none;
}
.av-stripes {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 4px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.avs1 { flex: 1; background: var(--gold); }
.avs2 { flex: 1; background: var(--red); }
.avs3 { flex: 1; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
.av-badge {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1px;
  right: 30px;
  background: var(--gold);
  padding: 16px 28px;
}
.av-badge-text {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: var(--black);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.av-badge-num {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--black);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-top: 2px;
}

/* SERVICES */
#services {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  background: var(--cream);
  position: relative;
}
.section-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-end;
  margin-bottom: 80px;
}
.section-label {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  color: var(--red);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.section-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -3px;
  color: var(--black);
}
.section-sub {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.4);
  max-width: 280px;
  text-align: right;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: rgba(10,10,10,0.1);
}
.service-card {
  background: var(--cream);
  padding: 52px 40px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: background 0.4s;
  cursor: default;
}
.service-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0; left: 0;
  width: 0; height: 2px;
  background: var(--gold);
  transition: width 0.4s ease;
}
.service-card:hover { background: var(--black); }
.service-card:hover::after { width: 100%; }
.service-card:hover .svc-num-big { color: rgba(201,168,76,0.08); }
.service-card:hover .svc-title-card { color: var(--white); }
.service-card:hover .svc-desc-card { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }
.service-card:hover .svc-link { color: var(--gold); border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3); }
.svc-num-big {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 72px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.05);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -4px;
  transition: color 0.4s;
  margin-bottom: -20px;
}
.svc-title-card {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--black);
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  transition: color 0.4s;
}
.svc-desc-card {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.5);
  line-height: 1.7;
  transition: color 0.4s;
}
.svc-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 28px;
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.35);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.1);
  padding-bottom: 3px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
}

/* PROCESS */
#process {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.process-bg-text {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 300px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
  white-space: nowrap;
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}
.process-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
  margin-top: 80px;
  position: relative;
}
.process-line {
  position: absolute;
  top: 44px;
  left: 12.5%;
  right: 12.5%;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--border);
  z-index: 0;
}
.process-step {
  padding: 0 24px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.ps-dot {
  width: 10px; height: 10px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  position: relative;
}
.ps-dot::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: -5px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.ps-num {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.ps-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.ps-body {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* WORKS */
#works {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  background: #0e0e0e;
}
.works-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 3px;
  margin-top: 80px;
}
.work-card {
  aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: default;
}
.work-card:first-child {
  grid-column: span 2;
  aspect-ratio: 16/7;
}
.wc-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  transition: transform 0.6s ease;
}
.work-card:hover .wc-bg { transform: scale(1.04); }
.wc1 { background: #1a1a1a; }
.wc2 { background: #111; }
.wc3 { background: #141414; }
.wc-pattern1 {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.wc-m-large {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(80px, 15vw, 180px);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
  letter-spacing: -8px;
}
.wc-bars {
  position: absolute;
  left: 40px;
  top: 0; bottom: 0;
  width: 8px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.wcb1 { flex: 1; background: var(--gold); }
.wcb2 { flex: 1; background: var(--red); }
.wcb3 { flex: 1; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
.wc-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(10,10,10,0);
  transition: background 0.4s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 40px;
}
.work-card:hover .wc-overlay { background: rgba(10,10,10,0.6); }
.wc-info {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(16px);
  transition: opacity 0.4s, transform 0.4s;
}
.work-card:hover .wc-info { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.wc-tag {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.wc-name {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white);
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}
.wc-geo {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.geo-circle {
  width: 180px; height: 180px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: absolute;
}
.geo-circle2 {
  width: 120px; height: 120px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: absolute;
}
.geo-cross-h {
  width: 60%;
  height: 1px;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
}
.geo-cross-v {
  position: absolute;
  width: 1px;
  height: 60%;
  background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
}
.geo-dot {
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
  position: absolute;
}

/* TESTIMONIALS */
#testimonials {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  background: var(--black);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.testimonials-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 40px;
  margin-top: 80px;
}
.testimonial-card {
  background: #111;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding: 48px 44px;
  position: relative;
}
.tc-quote {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 72px;
  color: var(--gold);
  line-height: 0.8;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  opacity: 0.3;
}
.tc-text {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.tc-author {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
.tc-avatar {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  background: var(--gold);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--black);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.tc-name {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: var(--white);
}
.tc-role {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.tc-stars {
  position: absolute;
  top: 48px; right: 44px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}
.testimonial-card.featured {
  background: var(--gold);
  border-color: var(--gold);
}
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-quote { color: var(--black); opacity: 0.15; }
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-text { color: rgba(10,10,10,0.8); }
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-name { color: var(--black); }
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-role { color: rgba(10,10,10,0.5); }
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-stars { color: var(--black); opacity: 0.5; }
.testimonial-card.featured .tc-avatar { background: var(--black); color: var(--gold); }

/* CTA SECTION */
#contact {
  padding: 140px 60px;
  background: var(--cream);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.cta-bg-m {
  position: absolute;
  right: -40px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 400px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.04);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -20px;
  pointer-events: none;
  user-select: none;
}
.cta-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  max-width: 640px;
}
.cta-label {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  color: var(--red);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.cta-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -4px;
  color: var(--black);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.cta-title span { color: var(--red); }
.cta-body {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.5);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  max-width: 460px;
}
.cta-form {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
}
.cta-input {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 18px 24px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.1);
  border-right: none;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--black);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.cta-input::placeholder { color: rgba(10,10,10,0.3); }
.cta-input:focus { border-color: var(--gold); }
.cta-submit {
  padding: 18px 36px;
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--gold);
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border: none;
  cursor: none;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
.cta-submit:hover { background: var(--red); }
.cta-promise {
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.35);
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  background: var(--black);
  padding: 80px 60px 40px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.footer-top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}
.footer-logo-area {}
.footer-logo {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: var(--white);
}
.footer-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
.footer-tagline {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  margin-top: 8px;
}
.footer-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 60px;
}
.footer-col-title {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  color: var(--gold);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.footer-col ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}
.footer-col a {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}
.footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
.footer-bottom {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding-top: 28px;
}
.footer-copy {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
}
.footer-social {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
}
.footer-social a {
  font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}
.footer-social a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.footer-stripes {
  display: flex;
  gap: 4px;
  align-items: center;
}
.fs { width: 24px; height: 3px; }
.fs1 { background: var(--gold); }
.fs2 { background: var(--red); }
.fs3 { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes marquee {
  from { transform: translateX(0); }
  to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
}
@keyframes scanLine {
  from { left: -100%; }
  to { left: 100%; }
}

.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(32px);
  transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
}
.reveal.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: none;
}
.reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

/* MOBILE */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
  nav.scrolled { padding: 16px 24px; }
  .nav-links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
  #hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
  .hero-stats { display: none; }
  .scroll-hint { left: 24px; }
  #about { padding: 80px 24px; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .about-visual { height: 300px; }
  #services { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .section-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .section-sub { text-align: left; }
  .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  #process { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .process-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .process-line { display: none; }
  #works { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .works-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .work-card:first-child { grid-column: span 1; aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
  #testimonials { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .testimonials-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  #contact { padding: 80px 24px; }
  .cta-form { flex-direction: column; }
  .cta-input { border-right: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.1); border-bottom: none; }
  footer { padding: 60px 24px 32px; }
  .footer-top { flex-direction: column; gap: 48px; }
  .footer-links { gap: 32px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">MONARCH<span>.</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#works">Works</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get a Quote</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="hero-stripes">
      <div class="hs-panel hs1"></div>
      <div class="hs-panel hs2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hs-accent"></div>
    <div class="hs-accent2"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Premium Design Studio</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      WE BUILD<br>
      <span class="gold">BRANDS</span><br>
      THAT <span class="red">RULE</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Logo design, brand identity &amp; graphic design crafted for businesses that refuse to be ordinary.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#services" class="btn-primary">Explore Services</a>
      <a href="#works" class="btn-secondary">View Our Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">150<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Brands Built</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">98<span>%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Satisfaction</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">5<span>★</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Avg Rating</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span class="scroll-text">Scroll to explore</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-section">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Logo Design</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Brand Identity</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Graphic Design</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Social Media Kit</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Visual Strategy</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Typography Systems</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Brand Guides</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Logo Design</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Brand Identity</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Graphic Design</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Social Media Kit</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Visual Strategy</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Typography Systems</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-text">Brand Guides</span><span class="marquee-dot"></span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div>
    <div class="about-label reveal">About Monarch Design</div>
    <h2 class="about-title reveal reveal-delay-1">We Don't Follow Trends.<br>We Set Them.</h2>
    <p class="about-body reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <strong>Monarch Design</strong> is a premium design studio dedicated to one mission: making your business look like the undisputed leader in your industry.
    </p>
    <p class="about-body reveal reveal-delay-2">
      We believe a great brand isn't just a logo — it's a <strong>complete visual kingdom</strong>. From the first impression to every touchpoint, we craft identities that command respect and inspire loyalty.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-visual reveal reveal-delay-3">
    <div class="av-frame"></div>
    <div class="av-inner">
      <div class="av-stripes">
        <div class="avs1"></div>
        <div class="avs2"></div>
        <div class="avs3"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="av-m">M</div>
    </div>
    <div class="av-badge">
      <div class="av-badge-text">Years of Excellence</div>
      <div class="av-badge-num">5+</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section id="services">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--black)">OUR<br>SERVICES</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub">Every service designed to make your brand the one people remember.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="services-grid">
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="svc-num-big">01</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Logo Design</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">A mark that stands alone. We create logos that are timeless, versatile, and impossible to forget — built to last decades, not seasons.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="svc-num-big">02</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Brand Identity</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">Colors, typography, patterns, and tone — your full visual language, unified into a system that scales from business card to billboard.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="svc-num-big">03</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Graphic Design</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">Posters, presentations, marketing materials, and more. Every piece designed with intention — making your message impossible to ignore.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal">
      <div class="svc-num-big">04</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Social Media Kit</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">Templates, covers, story formats, and post designs — all cohesive, all on-brand. So every post you publish looks like a professional campaign.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="svc-num-big">05</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Brand Strategy</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">We help you define your positioning, voice, and visual direction before a single pixel is placed. Strategy is the foundation of great design.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="svc-num-big">06</div>
      <div class="svc-title-card">Brand Guidelines</div>
      <p class="svc-desc-card">A complete manual documenting how your brand looks, speaks, and feels — so every designer, employee, and partner maintains the standard.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="svc-link">Start a project</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section id="process">
  <div class="process-bg-text">PROCESS</div>
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold)">How We Work</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">THE<br>PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)">Four steps to take your brand from ordinary to extraordinary.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="process-steps">
    <div class="process-line"></div>
    <div class="process-step reveal">
      <div class="ps-dot"></div>
      <div class="ps-num">Step 01</div>
      <div class="ps-title">Discovery</div>
      <p class="ps-body">We learn everything about your business, audience, and vision through a deep-dive consultation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="ps-dot"></div>
      <div class="ps-num">Step 02</div>
      <div class="ps-title">Concept</div>
      <p class="ps-body">We present multiple creative directions, each grounded in strategy and built around your goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="ps-dot"></div>
      <div class="ps-num">Step 03</div>
      <div class="ps-title">Refinement</div>
      <p class="ps-body">We refine the chosen direction together, perfecting every detail until it's exactly right.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="ps-dot"></div>
      <div class="ps-num">Step 04</div>
      <div class="ps-title">Delivery</div>
      <p class="ps-body">You receive all final files, full source files, and brand guidelines — ready to dominate your market.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WORKS -->
<section id="works">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold)">Portfolio</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">SELECTED<br>WORKS</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)">A glimpse of the brands we've built from the ground up.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="works-grid">
    <div class="work-card reveal">
      <div class="wc-bg wc1">
        <div class="wc-pattern1">
          <div class="wc-m-large">M</div>
        </div>
        <div class="wc-bars">
          <div class="wcb1"></div>
          <div class="wcb2"></div>
          <div class="wcb3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wc-overlay">
        <div class="wc-info">
          <div class="wc-tag">Brand Identity · Logo Design</div>
          <div class="wc-name">Monarch Studio — Full Identity System</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="work-card reveal">
      <div class="wc-bg wc2">
        <div class="wc-geo">
          <div class="geo-circle"></div>
          <div class="geo-circle2"></div>
          <div class="geo-cross-h"></div>
          <div class="geo-cross-v"></div>
          <div class="geo-dot" style="top:30%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
          <div class="geo-dot" style="top:70%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);background:#B22222"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wc-overlay">
        <div class="wc-info">
          <div class="wc-tag">Logo Design</div>
          <div class="wc-name">Geometric Mark — Precision Logo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="work-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="wc-bg wc3">
        <div class="wc-pattern1">
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;align-items:center">
            <div style="font-family:'Unbounded',sans-serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:900;color:rgba(201,168,76,0.15);letter-spacing:4px">ROYAL</div>
            <div style="width:120px;height:1px;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.15)"></div>
            <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);font-style:italic;letter-spacing:6px">STUDIO</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="wc-overlay">
        <div class="wc-info">
          <div class="wc-tag">Typography · Brand</div>
          <div class="wc-name">Royal Studio — Editorial Identity</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section id="testimonials">
  <div class="section-header reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold)">Testimonials</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">WHAT CLIENTS<br>SAY</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="section-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)">Real words from real businesses transformed by Monarch Design.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="testimonials-container">
    <div class="testimonial-card featured reveal">
      <div class="tc-quote">"</div>
      <div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="tc-text">Working with Monarch Design was the best investment we made for our business. Our brand went from something we were embarrassed about to something we're incredibly proud of.</p>
      <div class="tc-author">
        <div class="tc-avatar">SK</div>
        <div>
          <div class="tc-name">Sarah K.</div>
          <div class="tc-role">Founder, Lumière Beauty</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="tc-quote">"</div>
      <div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="tc-text">The logo they created for us is pure perfection. Every single person who sees it asks who designed it. Monarch Design delivered beyond what I thought was possible.</p>
      <div class="tc-author">
        <div class="tc-avatar">AM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="tc-name">Ahmed M.</div>
          <div class="tc-role">CEO, Atlas Real Estate</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="tc-quote">"</div>
      <div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="tc-text">Fast, professional, and incredibly talented. They understood exactly what I needed — and then exceeded every expectation. I'll never go anywhere else for design work.</p>
      <div class="tc-author">
        <div class="tc-avatar">LB</div>
        <div>
          <div class="tc-name">Leila B.</div>
          <div class="tc-role">Director, Bloom Agency</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="tc-quote">"</div>
      <div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div>
      <p class="tc-text">Our social media engagement tripled after the rebrand. When your visuals are this strong, the results speak for themselves. Monarch Design is on another level.</p>
      <div class="tc-author">
        <div class="tc-avatar">KN</div>
        <div>
          <div class="tc-name">Karim N.</div>
          <div class="tc-role">Founder, Noir Apparel</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA / CONTACT -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="cta-bg-m">M</div>
  <div class="cta-content reveal">
    <div class="cta-label">Ready to Start?</div>
    <h2 class="cta-title">YOUR BRAND<br><span>DESERVES</span><br>THE CROWN.</h2>
    <p class="cta-body">Tell us your email and we'll get in touch within 24 hours to discuss your project — no commitment, no pressure.</p>
    <div class="cta-form">
      <input type="email" class="cta-input" placeholder="Your email address...">
      <button class="cta-submit">Get a Free Quote</button>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-promise">Free consultation · No commitment · Response within 24 hours</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-top">
    <div class="footer-logo-area">
      <div class="footer-logo">MONARCH<span>.</span></div>
      <div class="footer-tagline">Where Brands Become Royalty</div>
      <div class="footer-stripes" style="margin-top:24px">
        <div class="fs fs1"></div>
        <div class="fs fs2"></div>
